# Never commit rendered secrets or local state.
*.env
.config/linear-tui/env
**/.DS_Store

# OpenTofu / Terraform local state and generated bootstrap inputs.
**/.terraform/
**/terraform.tfstate
**/terraform.tfstate.*
**/*.tfplan
**/*.tfvars
**/*.auto.tfvars.json
provisioning/**/.generated/

# Agent telemetry — never versioned
.claude/
**/__pycache__/
